==Awards and honours==
* [[Iron Cross]] (1939)
** 2nd Class (17 September 1939){{sfn|Thomas|1998|p=107}}{{refn|According to Röll on 9 November 1939.{{sfn|Röll|2010|p=154}}|group="Note"}}
** 1st Class (10 May 1940){{sfn|Thomas|1998|p=107}}
* [[German Cross]] in Gold on 5 June 1942 as ''[[Hauptmann]]'' in the II./Jagdgeschwader 26{{sfn|Patzwall|Scherzer|2001|p=323}}
* [[Front Flying Clasp of the Luftwaffe]] for Fighter Pilots in Gold with Pennant "400"{{sfn|Berger|1999|p=236}}
* [[Combined Pilots-Observation Badge]]{{sfn|Berger|1999|p=236}}
* [[Knight's Cross of the Iron Cross with Oak Leaves and Swords]]
** Knight's Cross on 14 September 1940 as ''[[Oberleutnant]]'' and ''[[Staffelkapitän]]'' of the 7./Jagdgeschwader 26 "Schlageter"{{sfn|Fellgiebel|2000|p=319}}{{sfn|Von Seemen|1976|p=248}}{{refn|According to Scherzer as [[adjutant]] in the III./Jagdgeschwader 26 "Schlageter".{{sfn|Scherzer|2007|p=559}}|group="Note"}}
** 12th Oak Leaves on 7 May 1941 as ''Oberleutnant'' and ''Staffelkapitän'' of the 7./Jagdgeschwader 26 "Schlageter"{{sfn|Scherzer|2007|p=559}}{{sfn|Fellgiebel|2000|p=54}}{{sfn|Von Seemen|1976|p=25}}
** 19th Swords on 9 September 1942 as ''Hauptmann'' and deputy ''[[Geschwaderkommodore]]'' of Jagdgeschwader 51 "Mölders"{{sfn|Scherzer|2007|p=559}}{{sfn|Fellgiebel|2000|p=40}}{{sfn|Von Seemen|1976|p=14}}
* Mentioned five times in the [[Wehrmachtbericht]]
* [[Gold Medal of Military Valor|Medaglia d'oro al Valore Militare]] (7 May 1941){{sfn|Röll|2010|p=154}}

